==Usage== <!--T:6-->

<!--T:7-->
# Select two or more vertical dimensions.
# The first dimension defines the position. This dimension will not be move.
# There are several ways to invoke the tool:
#* Press the {{Button|[[Image:TechDraw_ExtensionPosVertChainDimension.svg|16px]] [[TechDraw_ExtensionPosVertChainDimension|Align Vertical Chain Dimensions]]}} button.
#* Select the {{MenuCommand|TechDraw → Attributes/Modifications → [[Image:TechDraw_ExtensionPosVertChainDimension.svg|16px]] Align Vertical Chain Dimensions}} option from the menu.
# The dimensions are aligned and their dimension texts are centered.

